---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Heading from "../ui/typography/Heading.astro";
import Text from "../ui/typography/Text.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="FAQ">
  <section class="faq-hero">
    <Heading as="h1" size="xl" maxLineLength={false}>Frequently Asked Questions</Heading>
    <Text as="p" size="lg" class="faq-hero__subtitle">
      Common questions about Kickstarter United, our contracts, and the 4-day
      work week.
    </Text>
  </section>

  <div class="faq-list">
    <details class="faq-item" open>
      <summary class="faq-item__q">What is Kickstarter United?</summary>
      <div class="faq-item__a">
        <Text as="p">
          Kickstarter United is the union that represents the employees of
          Kickstarter, PBC. We are part of
          <a href="https://www.opeiulocal153.org/">OPEIU Local 153</a>
          and are also associated with
          <a href="https://www.techworkersunion-1010.org/">OPEIU's Tech Workers Union Local 1010</a>
        </Text>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-item__q">How does the 4-day work week (4DWW) work at Kickstarter?</summary>
      <div class="faq-item__a">
        <Text as="p">
          Kickstarter embarked on a 4DWW 32 hour pilot in April of 2022. The
          premise of that pilot can be summarized by 100-80-100. That means 100%
          of the work is completed in 80% of the time for 100% of the pay. The
          important piece is that 100% of the work is getting done in less time.
          Same work done = same pay.
        </Text>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-item__q">Has the 4DWW been a success?</summary>
      <div class="faq-item__a">
        <Text as="p">
          Kickstarter management sure thinks so - they've talked about it
          extensively over the years - and we workers agree! Our output has
          remained the same but our work life balance has improved immensely and
          it's been a great recruiting tool for the company. Some folks even
          took pay cuts to come work a 4-day work week at Kickstarter.
        </Text>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-item__q">How is the 4DWW protected in the 2025 contract?</summary>
      <div class="faq-item__a">
        <Text as="p">
          Protecting the 4DWW was one of the key issues during our 2025
          contract negotiations and the 42-day strike that followed. Our
          <a href="/contracts/2025">2025 contract</a> includes strong
          protections for the 4-day work week, ensuring that the schedule
          Kickstarter and our workers have thrived under cannot be
          unilaterally changed by management.
        </Text>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .faq-hero {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: var(--ksru-space-sm);
    margin-block: var(--ksru-space-2xl) var(--ksru-space-xl);
  }

  .faq-hero__subtitle {
    color: color-mix(in oklch, currentColor, transparent 30%);
    text-wrap: balance;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .faq-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--ksru-space-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--ksru-space-2xl);
  }

  .faq-item {
    border: 1px solid var(--ksru-color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;

    @supports (corner-shape: squircle) {
      corner-shape: squircle;
      border-radius: 24px;
    }
  }

  .faq-item[open] {
    border-color: var(--ksru-color-border-hover);
  }

  .faq-item__q {
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: var(--ksru-space-md) var(--ksru-space-lg);
    font-family: var(--ksru-font-family-heading);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--ksru-space-md);
    transition: background-color 0.15s;
  }

  .faq-item__q::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-item__q::after {
    content: "+";
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 1.5rem;
    height: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ksru-emerald-500);
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .faq-item[open] .faq-item__q::after {
    content: "\2212";
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .faq-item__q:hover {
    background: var(--ksru-color-surface-hover);
  }

  .faq-item__q:focus-visible {
    outline: 3px solid var(--ksru-color-outline, currentColor);
    outline-offset: -3px;
  }

  .faq-item__a {
    padding: 0 var(--ksru-space-lg) var(--ksru-space-lg);
    color: color-mix(in oklch, currentColor, transparent 15%);
  }
</style>
